<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6743> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6743" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/3> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Propraetor in Sicily before 27, named on a coin of Melita (Head, HN2 883). Grant (59f.) suggests that he held command only in Melita in 36 as an officer in the fleet and exactor of an indemnity. See PIR(2) 1.220, no. 1122." .
